Detailed Description

cvmx_srio::_maint_rd_data

This register allows read access of the local SRIOMAINT registers. A write to the SRIO()_MAINT_OP register with the OP bit set to zero initiates a read request and clears the VALID bit. The resulting read is returned here and the VALID bit is set. Access to the register will not stall the RSL but the VALID bit should be read.

This register is reset by the h-clock reset.
